_sText:
About 2 years ago my roommate BigJR and I owned a CSS server called CALFun. CAL was derived from the school we go to Cal U of PA. 

BigJR asked me to make a simple Deathmatch map that he drew up. I had never used Hammer before and it was a lot of fun learning how to create calfun_deathmatch.

This is the 4th and final version of the map.

This was our most played map on our server.

I miss having the server but hopefully some people will get to enjoy the maps I made for it for a long time.
